@startuml
title UC-05 Cancel Booking (Penalty-Based System)

|Customer|
start
:Open booking details;
:Select "Cancel Booking";

|System|
:Check booking status;
:Evaluate cancellation policy;

if (Cancellation allowed?) then (Yes)

  :Check booking acceptance status;

  if (Booking already accepted?) then (Yes)
    :Calculate cancellation penalty fee;
    :Apply penalty to customer account;
    :Store penalty record for future bookings;

  else (No)
    :No penalty applied;
  endif

  :Update customer profile with cancellation history;
  :Mark customer as "Penalty Flagged" if applicable;

  |Garage Owner|
  :Receive cancellation notification;

  |System|
  :Update booking status to CANCELLED;

  |Customer|
  :View cancellation confirmation;

  |System|
  :When customer tries future booking:
  :Check penalty/foul status;

  if (Penalty exists?) then (Yes)
    :Show warning message:
    "Penalty fee will be added to this booking";
  else (No)
    :Proceed normally;
  endif

  stop

else (No)

  :Display "Cancellation Denied";
  stop

endif

@enduml